TPM2 Load() TPM Load()
TPM2 Unseal(Unbind)() TPM Unbind()
TPM2 Sign() TPM Sign()
TPM2 Quote() TPM Quote()
TPM2 CertifyCreation() TPM Sign()
TPM2 Sync Begin() TPM Unbind()
TPM2 Sync End() TPM Unbind()



